Pegang ini.

119
00:07:12,362 --> 00:07:13,293
Pegang.

120
00:07:15,155 --> 00:07:15,909
Aduk.

121
00:07:15,933 --> 00:07:17,198
Coba diaduk.

122
00:07:19,378 --> 00:07:19,794
Betul.

123
00:07:20,462 --> 00:07:22,037
Sekarang, dimakan.

124
00:07:22,711 --> 00:07:23,645
Makanlah.

125
00:07:27,669 --> 00:07:28,747
Pintar sekali.

126
00:07:29,415 --> 00:07:32,417
Jadi begitu. Sebelum dimakan,
diaduk dulu.

127
00:07:33,277 --> 00:07:34,281
Yeon Soo!

128
00:07:34,471 --> 00:07:35,473
Jung Soo!

129
00:07:35,842 --> 00:07:37,842
Lagi apa, kau tak turun?

130
00:07:40,281 --> 00:07:41,055
Jung Soo!

131
00:07:42,570 --> 00:07:43,418
Omo, omo!

132
00:07:44,775 --> 00:07:45,868
Dasar anak ini...

133
00:07:45,892 --> 00:07:47,569
Bocah ini.

134
00:07:47,593 --> 00:07:48,991
Aigoo, baunya.

135
00:07:49,015 --> 00:07:51,909
Aigoo, dasar.

136
00:07:56,615 --> 00:07:59,547
Aigoo. Kau ini mabuk berat.

137
00:07:59,571 --> 00:08:02,793
Kau kenapa?
Minum-minum seharian?

138
00:08:05,874 --> 00:08:07,612
Apa kau dicampakkan sama wanita?

139
00:08:08,108 --> 00:08:11,726
Atau apa yang tak bisa
kauceritakan sama ibu sendiri?

140
00:08:12,027 --> 00:08:12,817
Katakan saja.

141
00:08:13,233 --> 00:08:15,308
Kenapa kau selalu merokok
dan minum-minum seharian?

142
00:08:15,332 --> 00:08:18,306
Kamarmu ini banyak muntahan.
Ibu sampai tak kuat masuk sini.

143
00:08:19,273 --> 00:08:20,155
Jung Soo!

144
00:08:21,919 --> 00:08:24,485
Yeon Soo, makan dulu,
baru kerja.

145
00:08:32,339 --> 00:08:33,516
Kenapa cuma minum susu?

146
00:08:33,540 --> 00:08:35,269
Makan 8 suap nasi saja dulu.

147
00:08:36,137 --> 00:08:36,866
Aku sibuk.

148
00:08:41,354 --> 00:08:43,351
Hari ini Ibu nanti ketemu kau
di mal, ya.

149
00:08:43,375 --> 00:08:44,365
Bisa kita bertemu?

150
00:08:44,389 --> 00:08:45,332
Tidak, aku sibuk.

151
00:08:45,856 --> 00:08:47,356
Ayah, aku pergi.

152
00:08:47,380 --> 00:08:49,196
Aku tunggu di mobil.
Kalau Ayah sudah selesai, langsung keluar.

153
00:08:51,410 --> 00:08:52,911
Dasar anak itu...

154
00:08:56,657 --> 00:08:59,030
Ibu kenapa?

155
00:09:13,846 --> 00:09:15,327
Kau nanti hari ini,
ada operasi?

156
00:09:19,745 --> 00:09:20,498
Tidak ada?

157
00:09:24,747 --> 00:09:29,587
Hari ini aku mau kumpul-kumpul sama
teman SMA-ku.

158
00:09:29,611 --> 00:09:33,046
Habis itu, aku nanti pulang
bareng sama kau. Bagaimana?

159
00:09:33,070 --> 00:09:34,127
Kumpul-kumpul?

160
00:09:35,319 --> 00:09:36,259
Kumpul-kumpul liburan.

161
00:09:37,932 --> 00:09:40,835
Kami pernah memutuskan akan pergi liburan
sama-sama sebelum kami meninggal.

162
00:09:40,859 --> 00:09:42,647
Kami sudah merencanakannya
sejak 5 tahun lalu...

163
00:09:42,672 --> 00:09:44,678
...untuk menabung 200rb
won masing-masing.

164
00:09:44,702 --> 00:09:47,397
Kali ini, kami berencana
mau ke Vietnam.

165
00:09:47,421 --> 00:09:48,932
Tapi sepertinya rencana
itu batal.

166
00:09:49,429 --> 00:09:52,624
Setelah nanti ketemu mereka,
aku langsung menemui kau sorenya.

167
00:09:52,648 --> 00:09:53,414
Buat apa?

168
00:09:55,670 --> 00:09:57,272
Belakangan ini, aku tak bisa
buang air kecil.

169
00:09:57,853 --> 00:09:59,268
Entah apa karena ginekologis...,

170
00:09:59,268 --> 00:10:01,086
...atau karena gesekan
dengan dalamanku.

171
00:10:01,110 --> 00:10:05,180
Aku mau ke RS dan periksa
ke dr. Yoon.

172
00:10:05,180 --> 00:10:06,360
Ke RS lain saja.

173
00:10:06,384 --> 00:10:08,195
Ke RS mana lagi?

174
00:10:08,219 --> 00:10:10,315
Aku tak mau melebarkan
kakiku di depan orang asing.

175
00:10:10,339 --> 00:10:12,200
Aku lebih nyaman kalau
sama dr. Yoon.

176
00:10:12,224 --> 00:10:13,681
Tapi kalau untuk kasus seperti itu,
ke RS kecil saja bisa.

177
00:10:13,705 --> 00:10:15,128
Kenapa harus ke RS kami?

178
00:10:15,582 --> 00:10:18,522
RS kecil nanti ujung-ujungnya juga
akan merujukku ke RS besar.

179
00:10:18,921 --> 00:10:20,794
Ayah, sudah telat ini!

180
00:10:33,067 --> 00:10:35,674
Pokoknya nanti aku ke RS, ya.

181
00:10:49,939 --> 00:10:51,517
Apa mulutmu itu terkunci apa?

182
00:10:51,541 --> 00:10:53,339
Kenapa tak jawab pertanyaanku?

183
00:10:56,717 --> 00:10:58,489
Dasar kau!

184
00:10:58,513 --> 00:11:00,048
Beraninya kau!

185
00:11:00,072 --> 00:11:04,132
Kau berani-beraninya kasih makanan
anjing ke mertuamu ini!

186
00:11:04,156 --> 00:11:05,778
Sini kau!

187
00:11:05,802 --> 00:11:08,149
Ibu! Rambutku!

188
00:11:08,149 --> 00:11:08,741
Lepas!

189
00:11:15,131 --> 00:11:16,997
Aigoo, pintarnya.

190
00:11:17,021 --> 00:11:18,514
Bola putih.

191
00:11:33,173 --> 00:11:34,149
Ini.

192
00:11:34,173 --> 00:11:36,249
Itu kuning.

193
00:11:41,091 --> 00:11:42,798
Ini. Bola putih.

194
00:11:42,822 --> 00:11:44,217
Itu biru.

195
00:11:44,241 --> 00:11:46,601
Yang kusuruh itu bola putih.

196
00:11:48,816 --> 00:11:49,535
Ini.

197
00:11:49,736 --> 00:11:50,939
Itu merah.

198
00:11:53,401 --> 00:11:54,561
Tak mau lah aku!

199
00:11:55,107 --> 00:11:56,603
Kenapa tak mau?

200
00:11:57,535 --> 00:11:58,651
Kita jalan-jalan saja.

201
00:11:58,675 --> 00:12:00,162
Kemana?

202
00:12:00,186 --> 00:12:02,186
Aku lagi sibuk mengelap mangkok.

203
00:12:02,210 --> 00:12:03,993
Tak usahlah keluar.

204
00:12:05,897 --> 00:12:07,159
Ayo keluar./
Kumat lagi.

205
00:12:07,183 --> 00:12:09,183
Kumat lagi seperti anak kecil./
Ayo keluar saja.

206
00:12:09,709 --> 00:12:11,207
Ayo keluar, Ibu.

207
00:12:11,231 --> 00:12:12,476
Kenapa aku jadi ibumu?

208
00:12:12,500 --> 00:12:13,805
Aku ini menantumu.

209
00:12:13,829 --> 00:12:15,262
Kita takkan keluar.

210
00:12:16,782 --> 00:12:19,573
Kalau Ibu membereskan bola-bola itu,
baru kita jalan ke luar.

211
00:12:20,000 --> 00:12:23,809
Ayo ke luar. Ke luar.

212
00:12:25,224 --> 00:12:26,251
Ke luar.

213
00:12:29,847 --> 00:12:30,939
Ibu mau ke luar?

214
00:12:32,275 --> 00:12:32,963
Ya.

215
00:13:21,774 --> 00:13:24,597
Siapa? Siapa yang datang?

216
00:13:24,899 --> 00:13:26,702
Siapa lagi?

217
00:13:51,543 --> 00:13:52,733
Kemana kau?

218
00:13:53,309 --> 00:13:55,662
Kemana kau mau tinggali aku? Dasar kau!

219
00:13:57,476 --> 00:13:58,548
<i>Jung Cheol!</i>

220
00:13:58,572 --> 00:14:00,153
Jung Cheol!

221
00:14:00,177 --> 00:14:01,483
Nenek. Tenanglah.

222
00:14:01,507 --> 00:14:03,400
Menantumu nanti pulang lagi.

223
00:14:03,424 --> 00:14:05,424
Minumlah obat dulu./
Jung Cheol.

224
00:14:05,448 --> 00:14:08,255
Ajak aku! Ajak aku!

225
00:14:08,279 --> 00:14:09,427
<i>Ibu!</i>

226
00:14:09,451 --> 00:14:10,232
<i>Jangan pergi!</i>

